desc: Each pouch has 225 mg of plant-based caffeine, and each energy chew has 75 mg. That’s more caffeine and better taste than a shot and caffeine gum.

layout.text: Each gummy has 75 mg and 225 mg per pouch of plant-based, fast-acting energy.*
Our bold and original flavors made with real fruits include Elderberry and Tropical. Each will leave you with an enjoyable, long-lasting delicious taste!
Plant-based energy* with labels you can read and understand. Made with green coffee beans, real fruits and high in antioxidants from vitamin D.
Need a boost of caffeine to fuel your day? Take 1 gummy. Need even more for an action-packed schedule? Take 2 or 3.
